            <title>999 美元起零零科技 HOVERAir AQUA 无人机发布：可水中起飞、一键“召唤”自拍</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/877/506.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/877/506.htm</guid>
